# ACF Flexible Content Blocks

This directory contains all ACF flexible content block templates.

Each block should be named exactly as the ACF layout name (e.g., hero_section.php).

## Block Structure

Each block file should follow this structure:

```php
<?php
/**
 * Block: Block Name
 *
 * Description of what this block does.
 */

// Get ACF fields
$field_name = get_sub_field('field_name');

// Block markup
?>
<section class="block-name">
    <!-- Your block HTML here -->
</section>
```

## Usage

Blocks are automatically rendered by the `allmighty_render_blocks()` function in page.php.
